<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN" style="margin:0;padding:0;">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <title>重置密码 - MonkeyCode-AI</title>
  <meta name="color-scheme" content="light">
  <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light">
  <style>
    /* 基础重置与 Email 兼容性样式 */
    html, body {
      margin: 0 !important;
      padding: 0 !important;
      height: 100% !important;
      width: 100% !important;
      background: #f6f7fb;
      -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
      -ms-text-size-adjust: 100%;
    }
    img {
      border: 0;
      outline: none;
      text-decoration: none;
      -ms-interpolation-mode: bicubic;
      display: block;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
    }
    /* 容器与排版 */
    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      background: #f6f7fb;
      padding: 24px 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(18, 38, 63, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid #eef0f6;
    }
    .header {
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 24px 28px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f3f7;
    }
    .brand-icon {
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
    }
    .brand-name {
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #111827;
      letter-spacing: 0.2px;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 28px;
      color: #111827;
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "Heiti SC", "WenQuanYi Micro Hei", "Noto Sans CJK SC", sans-serif;
    }
    .title {
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: #0f172a;
    }
    .greeting {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #374151;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .desc {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      color: #4b5563;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .cta-wrap {
      margin: 24px 0 12px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #111827;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      padding: 12px 18px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }
    .btn:hover { opacity: .96; }
    .btn:active { opacity: .92; }
    .url-fallback {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      background: #f9fafb;
      border: 1px solid #eef0f6;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      word-break: break-all;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .tip {
      margin: 16px 0 0;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
    }
    .footer {
      padding: 18px 28px 28px;
      color: #94a3b8;
      font-size: 12px;
      border-top: 1px solid #f8fafc;
    }
    .footer a {
      color: #64748b !important;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    /* 深色模式适配（部分客户端支持） */
    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      html, body { background: #0b0e14 !important; }
      .wrapper { background: #0b0e14 !important; }
      .container { background: #0f1320 !important; border-color: #111728 !important; }
      .header { border-bottom-color: #111728 !important; }
      .brand-name { color: #e5e7eb !important; }
      .content { color: #e5e7eb !important; }
      .title { color: #f8fafc !important; }
      .greeting, .desc { color: #cbd5e1 !important; }
      .url-fallback { background: #0b0e14 !important; color: #9ca3af !important; border-color: #1f2937 !important; }
      .tip { color: #9aa3b2 !important; }
      .footer { color: #94a3b8 !important; border-top-color: #111728 !important; }
      .footer a { color: #a3b2c7 !important; }
      .btn { background: #2563eb !important; }
    }
    /* 移动端优化 */
    @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
      .content, .header, .footer { padding-left: 20px !important; padding-right: 20px !important; }
      .title { font-size: 18px !important; }
      .btn { width: 100% !important; text-align: center !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <!-- 主容器，兼容大多数邮件客户端 -->
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" class="container">
            <!-- 顶部品牌 -->
            <tr>
              <td class="header">
                <img src="https://monkeycode-ai.com/logo.svg" alt="MonkeyCode-AI" class="brand-icon" width="28" height="28">
                <div class="brand-name">MonkeyCode-AI</div>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 内容区域 -->
            <tr>
              <td class="content">
                <h1 class="title">重置您的密码</h1>
                <p class="greeting">
                  你好，{{if .user}}{{.user}}{{else}}用户{{end}}：
                </p>
                <p class="desc">
                  我们收到了您账户的重置密码请求。请点击下方按钮前往安全页面完成密码重置操作。
                </p>

                <div class="cta-wrap">
                  <a class="btn" href="{{.reset_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">前往重置密码</a>
                  <div class="url-fallback">
                    如果按钮无法打开，请将以下链接复制到浏览器地址栏访问：<br>
                    <a href="{{.reset_url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{.reset_url}}</a>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <p class="tip">
                  出于安全考虑，重置链接可能会在一段时间后失效。如果您未发起此请求，请忽略此邮件，您的账户将保持安全。
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <!-- 页脚 -->
            <tr>
              <td class="footer">
                本邮件由 MonkeyCode-AI 系统自动发送，请勿直接回复。<br>
                需要帮助？请访问
                <a href="https://monkeycode-ai.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">MonkeyCode-AI 官网</a>
                获取支持。
              </td>
            </tr>

          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </div>
</body>
</html>